Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.31,0:22:59.65,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}有着不同的世界的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.65,0:23:05.24,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我想要找出所有重要的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:07.99,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}亲眼地确认
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:11.37,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Please Please Me 请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.37,0:23:15.46,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我想要伸出双手拥抱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.46,0:23:19.42,EDCN-beasttamer,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Let me free 请露出笑容吧
